caption.text:
I didn't even speak much to you the last time we met. No wonder, today I feel sad for no reason maybe thats a sign that you will be gone forever
.
 I still remember when you gave me my favorite food before I returned to Jkt and said that I should study well and make my parents proud of me. I also remember everytime you visit me,  my aunt said that you miss me, then you smiled at me because I know you can' t say that word to me. And I remember when you send me the same food every week until I get sick of it, because you know that I like that food. I know when you scold and get angry at me, that because you love me. You never got angry  everytime I play with your curly hair, your arms and your wheel chair, you always ask me what food that I want you to made for me, everytime I go to your place you always told me to eat and eat, I remember you always ask me to cut your nails and I often feels lazy to cut it (because its so hard to cut your thick nails), you always told me to learn mandarin eventhough I hate it
.
You already give me a lot of things, lessons and loves, and I still can't repay it. I'm gonna miss your voice, foods, words and everything about you, I miss pushing your wheel chair, held your hand when you want to stand or sit. And of course i'm gonna miss you so much. Thankyou for everything, I know that now you already meet grandpa and your family in heaven, I hope you are happy in there. Thank you for being my grandma and my daddy's mom .
I'm so lucky to have you in my life, I love you emak.💕👵
